# pkg

> Package management utility for Termux
> More information: https://wiki.termux.com/wiki/Package_Management

- Upgrade all installed packages:

`pkg upgrade`

- Install a package:

`pkg install {string value: package}`

- Uninstall a package:

`pkg uninstall {string value: package}`

- Reinstall a package:

`pkg reinstall {string value: package}`

- Search for a package:

`pkg search {string value: package}`
